### How to Play

1. Run the program.
2. The maze will be displayed, with the character's starting position marked as `C`.
3. Enter a direction (up, down, left, or right) to move the character.
4. The game will update the maze and display the new character position.
5. If the character reaches the exit, the game will end and a congratulatory message will be displayed.
6. If the character tries to move through a wall or outside the maze, an error message will be displayed and the character will not move.
